prompt_text: Describe a new place you have visited recently.
content_text: Recently I visited Dubai with a couple of friends. It was my first international trip and it was a great experience, a one that I will never forget. We visited multiple places. Such as the Bush Khalifa, the Golden Gate. The. Jumeirah Beach and. The Palm Beaches as well. Also we visited the Dubai Mall where I got to meet and see. A couple of other friends who were also visiting Dubai. It was a great experience and.
